---
// "Sunsets & drinks" (EN) — Menorca after dark hub: sunsets, beach clubs,
// cocktail bars and clubs, with the map of every spot and the luxury transfer
// (don't drive). Same family as the Planner and "Calm sea".
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import NightlifeMap from "../../components/NightlifeMap.astro";
import SunTimes from "../../components/SunTimes.astro";
import SunsetDrinksFaq from "../../components/SunsetDrinksFaq.astro";
import NewsletterSignup from "../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro";

const alternates = {
  es: "/atardeceres-y-copas",
  en: "/en/sunsets-and-drinks",
  fr: "/fr/couchers-et-cocktails",
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sunsets & drinks"
  description="Menorca after dark, with judgement: the best sunsets, beach clubs, harbour cocktail bars and where to go out, with a map of every spot and how to get there without driving."
  locale="en"
  alternates={alternates}
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-prosa px-5 pt-12 sm:px-8 sm:pt-16">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-oro">Calma Society · Menorca</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl text-tinta sm:text-5xl">Sunsets &amp; drinks</h1>
    <p class="lead mt-5">
      The island as the light turns: the best sunsets —and the eastern sunrises too—, the beach
      clubs, the harbour cocktail bars and where to go dancing. With a map of every spot, its Google
      rating and, further down, what time the sun rises and sets month by month —and how to reach
      each one without driving.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-piedra-suave">
      On the sunset cliffs and around the harbours there's almost nowhere to park, and in summer it
      fills up at dawn. So the easiest —and safest at night— choice is to leave the car behind: we
      drive you there and pick you up with a private chauffeur, from the first sunset to the last
      cocktail. This is our selection, with judgement and without the crowds: only places we've
      checked one by one, with their real Google rating and the honest reason it's better to come
      without a car.
    </p>
  </div>

  <nav aria-label="Page sections" class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-prosa px-5 sm:px-8">
    <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm">
      <li><a href="#mapa" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-niebla bg-arena/40 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-piedra transition-colors hover:border-arcilla hover:text-arcilla">The map of the night</a></li>
      <li><a href="#horas-del-sol" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-niebla bg-arena/40 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-piedra transition-colors hover:border-arcilla hover:text-arcilla">Sun times</a></li>
      <li><a href="#preguntas" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-niebla bg-arena/40 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-piedra transition-colors hover:border-arcilla hover:text-arcilla">FAQ</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div id="mapa" class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-5xl scroll-mt-32 px-5 sm:px-8">
    <NightlifeMap locale="en" />
  </div>

  <div id="horas-del-sol" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-32">
    <SunTimes locale="en" />
  </div>

  <div id="preguntas" class="scroll-mt-32">
    <SunsetDrinksFaq locale="en" />
  </div>

  <NewsletterSignup variant="inline" />
</BaseLayout>
